<text top="1081" left="822" width="10" height="14" font="13"><b>3 </b></text>
<text top="1081" left="90" width="44" height="12" font="14">08-24515 </text>
<text top="1096" left="90" width="3" height="14" font="13"><b> </b></text>
<text top="132" left="90" width="365" height="17" font="3">that the people of Somalia are not allowed to suffer any </text>
<text top="150" left="90" width="136" height="17" font="3">more than they have. </text>
<text top="177" left="90" width="4" height="17" font="3"> </text>
